Sentencas: A new series of double perovskite oxides Sr2Fe1-xTixNbO6-delta (x = 0, 0.05 & 0.1) were prepared by traditional solid state reaction method and characterized by X-ray diffraction, scanning electron microscope (SEM), energy dispersive x-ray (EDX), ac impedance and dc four point using Van Der Pauw method.
Titulo: Synthesis, structure and electrochemical performance of double perovskite oxide Sr2Fe1-xTixNbO6-δ as SOFC electrode

Sentencas: The samples were sintered at 1200 degrees C for 12 h in air to get single phase.
